👉 Handling Specific Exception in JAVA

In Java , We can handle specific exceptions by typing mulitple catch blocks

try{
    // code
}catch(I/O Exception e){
    // code
}catch(Arithmetic Exception e){
    // code
}catch(Exception e){
    // code
}

Sample Code :

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Errors{
    public static void main(String[] args){
